OL,3,C'Oldest' victim of Horizon IT scandal
OL,4,Csays ordeal 'destroyed' her health
OL,6,FA woman thought to be the oldest
OL,7,Fvictim of the Horizon IT scandal said
OL,8,Fthe ordeal "destroyed" her health as
OL,9,Fshe celebrated the publication of an
OL,10,Finquiry report.
OL,12,FBetty Brown, 92, from County Durham,
OL,13,Fran the Annfield Plain Post Office
OL,14,Fnear Stanley with her late husband
OL,15,FOswall, in the 1990s and early 2000s.
OL,17,FShe claims his death was impacted by
OL,18,Fthe ordeal of missing hundreds of
OL,19,Fpounds each week in their accounts.
