OL,3,C'Oldest' victim of Horizon IT scandal
OL,4,Csays ordeal 'destroyed' her health
OL,6,FMs Brown told the PA news agency: "We
OL,7,Fhad a nice office, nice atmosphere,
OL,8,Fnice customers, and everything was
OL,9,Ffine, no problem.
OL,11,F"And then we were told about this
OL,12,Fwonderful advancement in technology,
OL,13,Fand we would get a system put in,
OL,14,Fcalled Horizon that would half the
OL,15,Fworkload ` which it didn't.
OL,17,F"So Horizon was put in, then the very
OL,18,Ffirst night, the balance was #500
OL,19,Fshort, but they thought something had
OL,20,Fbeen missed in the accounts or
OL,21,Fwhatever and that was just let go.
