OL,3,C'Oldest' victim of Horizon IT scandal
OL,4,Csays ordeal 'destroyed' her health
OL,6,F"Then it began eventually that there
OL,7,Fwas so many mistakes in the system
OL,8,Fthat it was concerning, and these
OL,9,Flosses were coming out in amounts of
OL,10,F#1,500, #1,600 every week, and we were
OL,11,Fhaving to put this money in and make
OL,12,Fit good, because that's what you sign
OL,13,Fup for."
OL,15,F"The stress was unbelievable. You
OL,16,Fwould go to bed at night and you
OL,17,Fcouldn't sleep," she added.
