OL,3,C'Oldest' victim of Horizon IT scandal
OL,4,Csays ordeal 'destroyed' her health
OL,6,FMs Brown said the ordeal caused her to
OL,7,Flose her voice and said the anxiety it
OL,8,Fcaused her husband disrupted his
OL,9,Fcancer treatment.
OL,11,FHe died a year after they sold the
OL,12,FPost Office, which Ms Brown said she
OL,13,Ffelt forced to do.
OL,15,FA damning report into the Post Office
OL,16,FHorizon IT scandal published on 8 July
OL,17,Ffound that at least 13 people may have
OL,18,Ftaken their own lives after being
OL,19,Faccused of wrongdoing.
