OL,3,C'Oldest' victim of Horizon IT scandal
OL,4,Csays ordeal 'destroyed' her health
OL,6,FThe report, issued as part of the long-
OL,7,Frunning inquiry into the faulty
OL,8,FHorizon IT system used in Post Office
OL,9,Fbranches, described the impact on
OL,10,Fsubpostmasters as "disastrous" and
OL,11,Fsaid it heard evidence from 59 others
OL,12,Fwho had also contemplated suicide as a
OL,13,Fresult of the pressures from the
OL,14,Fscandal.
OL,16,FApproximately 1,000 subpostmasters
OL,17,Fwere wrongfully prosecuted by the Post
OL,18,FOffice between 1999 and 2015 after the
OL,19,Ffaulty Legacy Horizon software made it
OL,20,Flook as though money was missing from
OL,21,Ftheir accounts.
