OL,3,C'Oldest' victim of Horizon IT scandal
OL,4,Csays ordeal 'destroyed' her health
OL,6,FTuesday's 162-page report, written by
OL,7,Finquiry chair Sir Wyn Williams, also
OL,8,Fconcluded Post Office bosses knew the
OL,9,FHorizon IT system had widespread
OL,10,Ffaults, but had "maintained the
OL,11,Ffiction" it was accurate for years.
OL,13,FMs Brown continues her campaign for
OL,14,Ffull compensation but said on Tuesday,
OL,15,Fafter the first tranche of the Horizon
OL,16,Finquiry's final report was published,
OL,17,Fthat she had an "amazing" day.
OL,19,F"Sir (Wyn) Williams has done a
OL,20,Fwonderful job," Ms Brown said.
