OL,4,Csays ordeal 'destroyed' her health
OL,6,F"He has felt the pain, he's felt the
OL,7,Fanxiety, he's felt the agony, he's
OL,8,Ffelt everything that subpostmasters
OL,9,Ffelt and he has been able to bring
OL,10,Fthat with all his skill into a
OL,11,Fmeaningful book.
OL,13,F"I hope that the Post Office will take
OL,14,Fthis on board."
